The paper discusses the understanding of factors that impact mobile app requirements by requirements engineers in the mobile app industry. This involves technical knowledge in mobile app development as well as knowledge in areas such as privacy, security, and law. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SE (Software Engineering), followed by cs.CY (Cryptography and Security), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
